# Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

## Sanity Configuration

```env
# Sanity Project ID - Get from: https://manage.sanity.io
VITE_SANITY_PROJECT_ID=YOUR_PROJECT_ID

# Sanity Dataset (default: production)
VITE_SANITY_DATASET=production

# React App Sanity Config (for React apps)
REACT_APP_SANITY_PROJECT_ID=YOUR_PROJECT_ID
REACT_APP_SANITY_DATASET=production
```

## Kendo License (Optional but recommended for production)

```env
VITE_KENDO_LICENSE_KEY=YOUR_LICENSE_KEY
```

Get your Kendo license from: https://www.telerik.com/kendo-react-ui

## Optional: Analytics

```env
VITE_GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID=GA_4_ID
VITE_SEGMENT_KEY=YOUR_SEGMENT_KEY
```

## Optional: External APIs

```env
VITE_AFFILIATE_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY
VITE_PRODUCT_API_URL=https://api.example.com
```
